FIELD INSPECTION REPORT: INS-BLR-02.
Location: Unit 1 Boiler Room B. Date: 2026-06-01. Inspector: Sarah Jenkins.
Asset: High Pressure Steam Boiler BLR-201 bypass valve. Findings: Bypass control valve VLV-301 did not seat fully. Detected steam bypass pressure bleed and severe mineral carbonate scale buildup on valve face ring. Relieving valve pressure tests are overdue. ASME certificate certification check is non-compliant.